# MAGIC   - Add a **study** → one row in `study_config`.
# MAGIC   - Add a **matching method** → one branch in `matching.py`.
# MAGIC   - Add a **model** → one branch in `modeling.py`.
# MAGIC   - **Zero job edits** in every case.
# MAGIC - The **one** condition task left is the **pass/fail data-quality gate** — which is what
